p%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Available%20for%20%2430.99&amp;short_url=aXdyMB&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>售价 30.99 美元</u></a>。</p></li><li><p><strong>减压挤压玩具</strong>。可爱又实用的压力消除器。请务必与疲惫的同事们分享对此的了解。这款<a href="https://zdcs.link/ak7ymn?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=fidget%20toy%20for%20adults%20is%20%2424.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=ak7ymn&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=fidget%20toy%20for%20adults%20is%20%2424.99&amp;short_url=ak7ymn&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>成人烦躁玩具售价 24.99 美元</u></a>，或者更傻的“calma llama”售价<a href="https://zdcs.link/avxyVx?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=%2413.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=avxyVx&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=%2413.99&amp;short_url=avxyVx&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>13.99 美元</u></a>。</p></li><li><p> <strong>LED 蓝牙无檐小便帽</strong>。对于礼物交换来说，这是一个很棒的举动：非常适合音乐爱好者、寒冷的天气，并且它满足了对独特物品的需求。我的意思是，如果有人自愿拥有其中一件，我会感到震惊。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/9lwyDX?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=Get%20one%20for%20%2419.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=9lwyDX&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Get%20one%20for%20%2430.99&amp;short_url=9lwyDX&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>仅需 30.99 美元即可购买一件</u></a>。</p></li></ul><p>为了了解更多，我收集了一些更<a href="https://lifehacker.com/entertainment/best-secret-santa-gift-ideas" target="_blank">古怪的礼物，这些礼物在这里并不糟糕</a>。</p><h2 id="charitable-donations">慈善捐款</h2><p>以某人的名义捐赠的慈善捐款对于行善者和热衷于社会事业的人们来说可能是有意义的。您可以通过各种非营利组织选择货币金额或象征性地收养动物或树木。打印一份定制证书，交给接受者，宣布您为纪念他们而捐款。</p><p> Lifehacker 总编辑<a href="https://lifehacker.com/author/meghanwalbert" target="_blank">Meghan Walbert</a>推荐<a href="https://zdcs.link/JyZon?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=One%20Simple%20Wish&amp;short_url=JyZon&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">One Simple Wish</a> ，这是一个允许您为寄养儿童实现愿望的组织。另一种选择是以某人的名义种一棵树， <a href="https://zdcs.link/prp14?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=which%20you%20can%20do%20here&amp;short_url=prp14&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">您可以在此处执行此操作</a>。</p><p>嘿，如果他们对慈善礼物很讨厌，那么他们首先应该反思一下为什么他们这么难买礼物。但希望，通过一点额外的深思熟虑和创造力，你可以让假期购物清单上最挑剔的东西变得亮起来。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/money/gifts-for-the-person-who-has-everything<dc:creator>梅雷迪思·迪茨</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category></item><item><title>我今天最喜欢的亚马逊优惠：第 10 代 iPad</title><guid ispermalink="false"> 01J4SBSDJPQDVJXSCXG0J26RPX</guid><pubDate> Thu, 19 Dec 2024 16:30:00 +0000</pubDate><description>对于大多数人来说最好的平板电脑价格已降至 250 美元的历史最低价。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01J4SBSDJPQDVJXSCXG0J26RPX/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我们可以通过此页面上的链接赚取佣金。交易定价和供货情况可能会在发布后发生变化。</p><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/aAbmYb?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=10th-generation%20iPad&amp;short_url=aAbmYb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">第十代iPad</a>被认为是苹果的入门级平板电脑，也是<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/the-best-tablets-you-can-buy-right-now" target="_blank">目前市场上最好的平板电脑之一</a>。现在，您可以以自发布以来的最低价格购买该设备：使用 29.01 美元的页面优惠券后，价格为<strong>249.99 美元</strong>，低于黑色星期五的 279.99 美元价格，比 450 美元的首发价便宜 200 美元。在查看了<a href="https://lifehacker.com/best-price-tracking-tools-1692745053" target="_blank"><u>价格比较工具</u></a>后，我可以说这是 iPad 自 2022 年发布以来达到的最便宜价格。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">第十代iPad</div><div class="mt-4 block font-sans text-sm font-medium leading-4 text-gray-900 md:mx-0 md:mt-2"></div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>279.00 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$349.00</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $70.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-cen